data.description: Desirable location for the adorable 3 bedroom 2 bath home sitting one block from the Gulf in the X FLOOD ZONE!  Home comes fully furnished with updated kitchen featuring sleek stainless steel appliances.   Home could be used as investment home or as your permanent residence.   Built in 2021, this home offers an open floor plan with split bedrooms.  A single car garage to house your vehicle, golf cart, beach gear and more as well as plenty of room to add a pool if you want.   Home faces Americus Ave where you can make additional parking, but since this large lot runs all the way to the road in the back, this is where the driveway and adorable back porch can be found.   A perfect blend of style and functionality near the beautiful Gulf of Mexico!
